nodes.text: TR-1004 was a stormtrooper who served the First Order. He was stationed at Major Kander Varak's bacta production plant on Tevel, guarding warehouse four with TR-4018. The Resistance member Finn, on a mission to Tevel, attempted to enter the warehouse inside the casing of a gonk droid, tricking both TR-1004 and TR-4018 into letting him inside.
